🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻<br />\n<br />\n請唔好忘記成個運動嘅基本方針 就係：和理》勇武》和理》勇武 我地一定要接力 純和理會步雨傘後塵 純勇武會步六七暴動後塵 我地一定要接力！一定要接力！一定要接力！記住要贏成個戰爭 而唔係一兩場戰役 今次唔可以再輸 輸左我地就依世都對唔住走左嘅烈士🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n1⃣0⃣月1⃣4⃣人權法就過❗<br />\n大家忍八日‼️忍八日就得‼️‼️"},{"pid":"9c63827c5b88f6f657096d88f17b96f32051d270","tid":1633363,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"我得一個訴求<br />\n私了淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e58660f4ddf17da9be6f90b0e64bac6cd3fae8","tid":1633363,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53b6d324a133a7b32d650e71aebbb4c2f11ce2fe","tid":1633363,"uid":128489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89d6a60653304998db90e2facd352e1812b13350","tid":1633363,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb89faa0435ff3f6c170362373ac2c8ea9f911b7","tid":1633363,"uid":106477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"肥彭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前睇住佢落區食蛋撻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c436be9edc930c99ccfe0e62dde7ad3032b5f449","tid":1633363,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a411896739baf09bd2ac81057d531ef2dce96ed0","tid":1633363,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"點解97前唔廢咗緊急法?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"有用咩？<br />\n港共都會搵另一條法例去做野"},{"pid":"48b71d8c8dd5613dcb237a6be6f7cb5f45a542db","tid":16